Cc: anton@enomsg.org
Cc: ccross@android.com
Cc: keescook@chromium.org
Cc: tony.luck@intel.com
Signed-off-by: Jiri Slaby <jslaby@suse.cz>
---
 fs/pstore/ram.c |    2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

--- a/fs/pstore/ram.c
